video.title: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Dawn
video.synopsis: Just because they're quadruplets, that doesn't mean these 10-year-olds always get along. But for all the bickering, they're loyal to the last.

episodes.synopsis: After a chemistry class melee, Anne decides the only way the quads can adopt the new puppy they want is to prove they can take care of it together.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: On the quads' 10th birthday they think they're too old for Tom's traditional appearance as "The Quadfather" and decide they each want their own party.
episodes.title: The Quadfather

episodes.synopsis: Nicky, Ricky and Dicky have a crush on a new girl in school. When Tom's ice dancing arch rival opens a sporting goods store, the quads declare war.
episodes.title: Get Sporty-er!

episodes.synopsis: Dawn's had enough of sharing a bedroom with her brothers, but there's something important missing in her fabulous new room -- Nicky, Ricky and Dicky!
episodes.title: Dawn Moves Out

episodes.synopsis: It's an epic battle when the quads' fight over the TV remote results in a week without television, and Tom's super remote has a few bugs to work out.
episodes.title: Remote Control Control

episodes.synopsis: The quads want to replace weird babysitter Tanya with the much cooler Josie, but an unauthorized party when Anne and Tom are out could ruin that plan.
episodes.title: Quad-ventures in Babysitting

episodes.synopsis: After Anne and Tom forbid the quads from watching a scary movie on TV, they do it anyway, then start to think their parents are turning into zombies.
episodes.title: Field of Brains

episodes.synopsis: When their dog becomes a media hero after stopping a store robbery, his original owner comes to claim him -- but that doesn't sit well with the quads.
episodes.title: The Sad Tail of Gary-Chip-Tiny Elvis-Squishy Paws

episodes.synopsis: Dawn is thrilled to be chosen for the girls' soccer team until she realizes there's a "mean team" initiation that requires her to make fun of Nicky.
episodes.title: I Got Your Back

episodes.synopsis: In the case of the unflushed toilet the quad detectives must solve the mystery or the family trip to the water park will go down the drain.
episodes.title: Poo Dunnit

episodes.synopsis: The Harpers are all looking forward to the Halloween dance, but nothing goes as planned, not even for Anne and Tom, who're hoping to change the past.
episodes.title: Scaredy Dance

episodes.synopsis: Dawn sells a bracelet Anne gives her to buy tickets to a fanfest. Meanwhile, Tom takes away the boys' video games and insists they enter a 10K run.
episodes.title: Take the Money and Run

episodes.synopsis: The quads get Christmas jobs at the store to make money for a new video game console, but competition quickly turns them from elfish to selfish.
episodes.title: Santa's Little Harpers

episodes.synopsis: The quads' plan for getting out of family game night backfires when they try to find some couple friends for Anne and Tom.
episodes.title: Family Matters

episodes.synopsis: After Ricky's classmates see his bear, Lieutenant Blueberry, the quads make a bet on who can go the longest without their childhood security items.
episodes.title: The Quad-Test

episodes.synopsis: Dawn retaliates when she learns her brothers have been keeping secrets from her, but when things escalate, can they get back to their circle of trust?
episodes.title: The Secret

episodes.synopsis: The school talent show is causing a lot of Harper family friction when Anne wants to retire their puppet theater and Dawn wants to change the routine.
episodes.title: Piggy, Piggy, Piggy & Dawn

episodes.synopsis: When they're given a Valentine's Day assignment to do something special for someone, the quads can't seem to hit the mark -- even with Cupid's arrows!
episodes.title: Valentime's Day

episodes.synopsis: Five annual checkups ... five times banned from a doctor's office. The quads are hoping this year's visit will be perfect, with a cookie tower reward.
episodes.title: M.D. Day

episodes.synopsis: After Ricky is pressed into doing a magic trick that gets him grounded, his siblings sneak him into a party where a magician does a disappearing act.
episodes.title: Abraquadabra

episodes.synopsis: While the quads argue about how to tackle their group history presentation, they learn their family has a surprisingly intriguing history.
episodes.title: Wanted: The Sugar Beet Gang

episodes.synopsis: Eager to draw more readers to her school blog, Dawn writes a juicy column about the local urban legend known as Pigfoot.
episodes.title: Urban Legend Outfitters

episodes.synopsis: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky and Dawn find their social status challenged by a competitive rival with an enviable hangout space.
episodes.title: No Ifs, Ands, or But-ers

episodes.synopsis: Already swamped with activities and extracurriculars, Dawn finds yet another passion to pursue: the tuba.
episodes.title: Do-It-All Dawn

episodes.synopsis: The quads' plan to pretend they don't know each other has surprising consequences at summer camp.
episodes.title: Unhappy Campers

episodes.synopsis: It's sibling versus sibling as Ricky faces off against the upstart Dawn to become their new class president.
episodes.title: Harpers for President

episodes.synopsis: Tom and Anne take Nicky, Ricky, Dicky and Dawn to the mall, where the quads get into trouble while enjoying their newfound freedom.
episodes.title: Mall in the Family

episodes.synopsis: The quads set out to sell Tom's wild idea for a shoe prototype. But is there a corporate spy in their midst?
episodes.title: Sweet Foot Rides

episodes.synopsis: After Nicky, Ricky and Dicky ruin Dawn's dreams of meeting WNBA star Candace Parker, the three boys try to make amends.
episodes.title: I Want Candace

episodes.synopsis: The quads set up their own court to resolve conflicts among themselves. But what starts out as a good idea turns into something a bit less admirable.
episodes.title: Quad Court

episodes.synopsis: Nicky, Dicky and Dawn conspire to teach the all-knowing Ricky a lesson about superstitions, but their plan works a little too well.
episodes.title: She Blinded Him With Science (Bob)

episodes.synopsis: Internet fame goes to Nicky's head after a video of him pretending to be a superhero goes viral.
episodes.title: The Mighty Quad Squad

episodes.synopsis: While vacationing in Hollywood, the quads get mixed up in a mysterious -- and dangerous -- case of mistaken identity.
episodes.title: Go Hollywood

episodes.synopsis: While Anne's away at a spa, the quads rent out the garage to a loud-as-thunder band in hopes of making some money.
episodes.title: Rock n Rules

episodes.synopsis: Tom and Anne decide to leave the quads alone without a babysitter, but it doesn't take long before the dog escapes and chaos reigns.
episodes.title: Doggy Door Afternoon

episodes.synopsis: Seeking some alone time from her brothers, Dawn enrolls in an activity she thinks they'll have no interest in -- ballet.
episodes.title: Ballet and the Beasts

episodes.synopsis: When Ricky gets upset that his siblings don't take the sport of mini-golf seriously, he finds a new crew of snobby friends who do.
episodes.title: Quaddy-shack

episodes.synopsis: While at the movies to see the latest blockbuster, the quads worry their parents may make them look uncool.
episodes.title: The Quad-plex

episodes.synopsis: Dawn is alarmed -- to put it mildly -- when she learns that Nicky, Ricky and Dicky may all be developing feelings for Mae.
episodes.title: Three Men and a Mae B.

episodes.synopsis: Longing to be part of the popular crowd at school -- but wary that Ricky might hurt their chances -- the other quads come up with a plan.
episodes.title: A Brief Case of Popularity

episodes.synopsis: While Ricky struggles to embrace the absence of guidelines in art class, Dawn searches for ideas to make the Spring Festival a success.
episodes.title: The Tell-Tale Art

episodes.synopsis: When a mysterious new kid moves in next door, the quads try to befriend her in hopes of gaining access to her awesome treehouse.
episodes.title: New Kid on the Block

episodes.synopsis: Desperate to avoid missing out on the big class trip to the museum, Dawn hides her illness with a little help from her brothers.
episodes.title: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Sicky

episodes.synopsis: After Dawn discovers that Nicky, Ricky and Dicky are reading her diary, she schemes to get even on them by penning fake entries.
episodes.title: Diary of an Angry Quad

episodes.synopsis: Hollywood action star JT Steele moves into the quads' house to research a role. His only request: don't tell their friends he's there.
episodes.title: Mission: Un-Quaddable
This Little Piggy Went to the Harpers
Whats the Worst That Quad Happen?
I Want My Mae B. Back
To Be Invited or Not to Be
The Wonderful Wizard of Quads Part 1
The Wonderful Wizard of Quads Part 2
